Ah, another historical recounting. One might wonder why we bother, given how little humanity seems to learn from it. But since you've apparently found yourself in need of a detailed dissection of the [1992 United Kingdom general election](/1992_United_Kingdom_general_election), consider this an offering. Just don't expect me to pretend it was anything less than a profoundly illustrative moment in the grand tapestry of political misdirection and public surprise.

